Solution is in 3 steps :-
1) Traverse all boundary 0s and make them and all their connected 0s 1
2) Now traverse in matrix if you find a 1 that means it was previously a 0 which was not connected by X on all 4 directions or it was not connected to a valid 0 . Therefore make them 0 again. 
3) If you found a 0 that means it was a valid 0(i,.e connected by X on all 4 directions) therefore make it X.

