- Add all the elements of the ArrayList li to the PriorityQueue ans.

- Use a while loop to remove elements from the PriorityQueue ans until the kth smallest element is found or the PriorityQueue is empty. The loop decrements the value of k with each iteration.

- If the kth smallest element is found, store it in the variable val.

Return the value of val as the kth smallest element in the binary search tree.

