**APPROACH**
* Let us assume that we are on some `i`th element of the array.
* We were successfullly able to create each and every number till the range `arr[i]-1` by taking some numbers from arr in the range `0` to `i-1`. 
* Hence after choosing `arr[i]` we can create numbers from `0` to `arr[i]-1 + arr[i]` . 
	* Extra `arr[i]+1 to arr[i]+arr[i] -1` can be created by using `some numbers` and `arr[i]`
* If we are able to create numbers upto `arr[i]-1` 
	* No need to patch
* Else 
	* patch it with whatever numbers we are able to make +1 i.e `sum+1`


