Basic idea is to check every nid from 1 to n.
If number from nums is too large, then we need to patch nid itself, otherwise we can use nums[i].
we know that 1 to nid -1 all meet requirements. Adding nid or nums[i] will extend this range to nid + (nid or nums[i]) - 1. Then we start next check at nid + (nid or nums[i]).

